On 28 Jun 1997 09:05:49 +1000, Steve Talley wrote:

Just a couple of optimisations:

:#!/bin/zsh
: 
:IFS="
:"
: 
:i=1;
:for line in `cat file`

 for line in `< file`

:do
:    x[$i]=$line
:    i=`expr $i + 1`

     let i++

:done
